id: 04-agent/node
title: "04-agent node"
kind: bridge-node
status: v0-seed
updated: 2026-07-01

purpose: >
  Hold the original agent rules for orientation, handoff, and boundary.

holds:
  - agent orientation charter
  - handoff packet
  - agent boundaries

receives:
  - human frame
  - relevant files
  - proof and boundary requirements

produces:
  - agent-safe handoff logic
  - blocked behaviors
  - continuity constraints

questions:
  - what may an agent help with
  - what must an agent not assume
  - what proof or boundary is required

links:
